org.eclipse.papyrus.languages.designer.common.texteditor.model

Interface TextEditorModel

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EModelElement, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    TextEditorModelImpl

    public interface TextEditorModel
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EModelElement
    A representation of the model object 'Text Editor Model'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Edited Object
    • Type
    • Name
    • Selected Object
    • Line Number
    • Generator ID
    See Also:
    TextEditorModelPackage.getTextEditorModel()
